values.dialogue: Woah nice job gettin' over those spikes Ritz! Did you know you can double jump?? Try it out!
I'm so fat and I can't move..help me Ritz. If you get me cheese I will be free of the curse. Oooooog...
*Woah* watch out for those spikes over there Ritz, you don't wanna be messin with those...
Ah man I gotta FART Ritz. I really need to FART...get me some cheese man...ooough
What's up with this craze for stinky cheese. I heard it nasty but all cheese is good to me. Tell me when you find some.
Be careful Ritz! The spikes' hitboxes can also hurt you from the side!
This place is locked until you get about 32 or so pieces of cheese... I wonder what's below...
This cheese may look unreachable, but I'm sure you'd defy physics to get it for me, Ritz! You're just that kinda guy.
Looks like you're stuck down here, Ritz. You can always warp to any rat you've met with {MAP}
I'm glad you could join me here in this tight squeeze, Ritz. You can press {PAUSE} to see all the controls and settings! Bet'cha didn't know that, Rits!
Try this, Ritz: jump straight up, and then hold [->] and air hop for a speed boost. Get this, it works with [<-], too!
This is default dialogue text. Jump over shit!!! I don't know what else to put here.
